cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with the problem of object tracking using multiple drones equipped with cameras. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes an agent sharing network, which involves self-supervised learning and fusion of views from multiple drones, indicating a possible connection to robotics and control (cs.RO). The use of deep learning techniques for tracking and fusion suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with video data and proposes evaluation metrics, indicating a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
